snippet.title: Devil's Derby - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
The hordes are rising, only you stand in their way. Shoot, grind, slide, and jump your way around a multi-layered level against endless legions of demons, fiends, and monsters.

Rise, fall, and rise again. Can you survive the Devil's Derby?

Wistlist now:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3121580/Devils_Derby
